{
  "number": 458,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/458",
  "title": "Non-instant search box",
  "body": "I think we should also provide our users the ability to not trigger the search at each keystroke but rather once `<Enter>` has been pressed.\n\nI was thinking about patching the `searchBox` widget with something like:\n\n```\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\n    container: '#q',\n    // [...]\n    instant: false // will only trigger the search when <Enter> is pressed\n  })\n);\n```\n",
